snippet.title: Best VGM 1191 - Devil May Cry 3 - Devils Never Cry (Ending)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 477 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5niLxq7_yN4

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation 2
Devil May Cry 3 (2005)
Devils Never Cry
Tetsuya Shibata, David Baker & Shawn McPherson
